ckquote><br />\n韓仔tom告老師？</blockquote><br />\n潮未</blockquote><br />\n你對眼濕咗</blockquote><br />\n知唔知點解</blockquote><br />\n喊到baba聲</blockquote><br />\n死返入被竇屌西啦</blockquote><br />\n咁熱點屌"},{"pid":"58c73768eccdc6590d690a50da6c849b13b0f5a5","tid":423214,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n有樓</blockquote><br />\ntom房ok?</blockquote><br />\n韓仔tom告老師？</blockquote><br />\n潮未</blockquote><br />\n你對眼濕咗</blockquote><br />\n知唔知點解</blockquote><br />\n喊到baba聲</blockquote><br />\n死返入被竇屌西啦</blockquote><br />\n咁熱點屌</blockquote><br />\n凍熱你都搵唔到窿啦廢鳩"},{"pid":"98b4811dd5e29c3f70b42ad86af9b0c77e811cde","tid":423214,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n有樓</blockquote><br />\ntom房ok?</blockquote><br />\n韓仔tom告老師？</blockquote><br />\n潮未</blockquote><br />\n你對眼濕咗</blockquote><br />\n知唔知點解</blockquote><br />\n喊到baba聲</blockquote><br />\n死返入被竇屌西啦</blockquote><br />\n咁熱點屌</blockquote><br />\n凍熱你都搵唔到窿啦廢鳩</blockquote><br />\n我想入你個系"},{"pid":"de5f51f4bf0ae914f5c67c2b72aa7c8d6b465678","tid":423214,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n韓仔tom告老師？</blockquote><br />\n潮未</blockquote><br />\n你對眼濕咗</blockquote><br />\n知唔知點解</blockquote><br />\n喊到baba聲</blockquote><br />\n死返入被竇屌西啦</blockquote><br />\n咁熱點屌</blockquote><br />\n收兵, 扮單身, 話自己係PTGF, 派帽, 一腳踏兩船, 講得出既都做齊<br />\n我真係咁差? 一條仔換一條仔, 而我每次就只可以做後備, 由隱形正印變第三者<br />\n以前我講左好多地方想同你去, 你最後同左表姐去, 都唔同我呢個所謂既男友去<br />\n我dump左你既手信, 為左補償你, 我話請你去旅行, 一齊去買過, 但你唔制<br />\n我知自己鬧得你太勁, 想請你食好D, 兩個人開心下, 你都係唔制<br />\n我知你驚俾我請左, 會拎出黎講, 但樣樣野都計住, 真係一段關係黎?<br />\n如果一段關係入